"#\" class=\"btn\">View Details</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x300/DDDDDD/999999?text=Jacket+D\" alt=\"Chic Jacket D\">\n                    <h3>Minimalist Blazer</h3>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$150.00</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">View Details</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x300/E0E0E0/A0A0A0?text=Skirt+E\" alt=\"Pencil Skirt E\">\n                    <h3>Refined Pencil Skirt</h3>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$70.00</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">View Details</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x300/C0C0C0/707070?text=Cardigan+F\" alt=\"Knitted Cardigan F\">\n                    <h3>Soft Knit Cardigan</h3>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$110.00</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">View Details</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 ChicWardrobe. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <div class=\"social-links\">\n                <a href=\"#\">Facebook</a> |\n                <a href=\"#\">Instagram</a> |\n                <a href=\"#\">Pinterest</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}